https://gemini.google.com/gems/create

Gemini Gems are custom, mini versions of Gemini that you can create and personalize to act like dedicated experts for specific everyday tasks, such as a private coding coach, a workout planner, or a creative writing assistant. You benefit from them because you can give them highly specific instructions, custom knowledge files, and a preferred tone just once, saving you from typing the same background information every time you start a new chat. While they are highly customizable bots that can remember your specific instructions and follow complex workflows, they are generally seen as specialized AI assistants rather than fully autonomous AI agents because they still rely on you to start the conversation and guide them step-by-step.
